{"id":2292,"date":"2024-11-28T19:55:56","date_gmt":"2024-11-28T19:55:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2292"},"modified":"2024-12-01T03:13:46","modified_gmt":"2024-12-01T03:13:46","slug":"move-deleter","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/move-deleter\/","title":{"rendered":"Move Deleter (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left widesecond\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Epidimy Town<\/strong> &#8211; Inside of the house northwest of the Epidimy Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Allows you to delete any Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s moves, including HMs<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>N\/A<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>Free<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Epidimy Town Pokemon Center and enter the house to your northwest.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-house-northwest-of-the-epidimy-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the house northwest of the Epidimy Town Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the house northwest of the Epidimy Town Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Move Deleter is the only NPC inside the house.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-move-deleter.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Move Deleter. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Move Deleter.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<p>As the name suggests, the Move Deleter allows you to select a Pok\u00e9mon and to delete any move it knows without any cost. This includes HM\/TM moves and those the Pokemon naturally learned.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-n